54
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:46,128
Oh. Right. I still owe for those flowers.

55
00:02:47,613 --> 00:02:50,753
Oh, relax, Pam! You'll still
make it to weight watchers!

56
00:02:50,753 --> 00:02:51,730
Problem here, Dana?

57
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:53,761
Oh, great. Now the pips are here.

58
00:02:54,012 --> 00:02:56,810
It's Solis again.
She's holding up traffic.

59
